window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Sometimes two broken pieces make a whole. He's the one she's always loved. She's the one he could never have.</p> <p>A forbidden night of passion resulted in years of heartbreak when he walked away. Now she's in danger and needs his help.</p> <p>Trust doesn't come easy for FBI Agent Nick Stone, especially when it comes to love, but he'll risk it all for Katelyn Slade.</p> <p>Including his heart.</p> <p>Bullets fly, betrayals are exposed, and the flames from their past ignite.</p> <p>His protection might be what saves her, but in the end, she will be his salvation.</p> <p><b>Contains mature themes.</b></p>"; 
